{"tid":1997664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［正確心態］如果黃金週吸引到更多鋪頭話自己黃，就算為錢都好，都唔排斥，仲樂見其成","createTime":"2020-05-01T21:41:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T01:11:15.000Z","uid":31215,"like":179,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"9bf10554d6bac8fe388b349ee7e6c53b3bd4d46e","tid":1997664,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T21:41:32.000Z","msg":"今次黃金週搞得幾好<br />\n如果咁多左商店聲稱自己黃<br />\n就算假都好都唔使批鬥住<br />\n淨係喺黃藍地圖post好證據，幾時做過咩就足夠<br />\n而且都可以幫襯<br />\n<br />\n相信大家都傾向<br />\n深黃/一早黃 &gt; 淺黃 &gt; 後期黃/偽黃 &gt;中立<br />\n咁黎消費<br />\n淺藍深藍不予考慮<br />\n<br />\n中共成日要人愛國<br />\nAngelababy 、的士陳、梁家輝嗰啲一睇就知為左錢先撐警、先post 一點不能少<br />\n但大陸同小粉紅唔會屌佢地偽愛國，食愛國饅頭<br />\n仲好歡迎佢地咁做<br />\n會射住班假人<br />\n咁先營造到好多人愛國嘅氣勢<br />\n<br />\n如果我地想下年有幾萬間商店<br />\n就唔好鬥黃<br />\n接受有鋪頭喺因為商業誘因先加入<br />\n偽黃都唔打擊<br />\n視為可幫襯名單，不過優先度較低<br />\n<br />\n海納百川，聲威先可以壯大"},{"pid":"a0ef70c29c8797b72f9e0e894f56eb6851309132","tid":1997664,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T21:42:37.000Z","msg":"清晨有冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db60c5f9dab7f431301c503d0756be5cd87b4d05","tid":1997664,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T21:43:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e36dd6b8a95b0f467b68e3dcd8f61079cb531f","tid":1997664,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T21:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02362e555f74fcbaf471487fc7f664cdfbd470d5","tid":1997664,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T21:44:27.000Z","msg":"認同請幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 