多人愛國嘅氣勢<br />\n<br />\n如果我地想下年有幾萬間商店<br />\n就唔好鬥黃<br />\n接受有鋪頭喺因為商業誘因先加入<br />\n偽黃都唔打擊<br />\n視為可幫襯名單，不過優先度較低<br />\n<br />\n海納百川，聲威先可以壯大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:01:46.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"b459899541c866fba9a45e7a4c24c2a066eebfd0","tid":1997664,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:01:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"918fe63fda18404b376004cdc3a73145656d0e06","tid":1997664,"uid":33336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:03:48.000Z","msg":"中共都係用同樣手法要大機構收聲，未必要佢真心紅/藍，國泰就係個例子<br />\n<br />\n用番同一個方法對藍店一樣得，所以咪撚再鬥黃，偽黃放在心裡，去唔去支持就自己決定，唔需要批鬥"},{"pid":"eacdc8ef53e44106b0032e11bea97f35b4461b73","tid":1997664,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc84950714f6033447aec047ca8e7d9b3a78a73","tid":1997664,"uid":312859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:05:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42bf5d19e558907f4d2b46538783e88a5cc72d4f","tid":1997664,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa6556008fe606542e26abf29a578965eb64c401","tid":1997664,"uid":259520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T02:18:34.000Z","msg":"依家要求黃店呢樣個樣.<br />\n又話唔夠黃.根本5毛.<br />\n<br />\n未做大個餅就要求多. 根本就ON 9 行為.<br />\n就好似一個演員拍一套戲紅少少,就扮大支爺.<br />\n結果米令人討厭, 本來可能會紅起, 但on 9 攪到失機會."},{"pid":"c6902bb5d10a44fc2ae7d43c4f78eebdad0b1e3a","tid":1997664,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa6556008fe606542e26abf29a578965eb64c401","tid":